Class TargetData

java.lang.Object
org.strykeforce.deadeye.TargetData
Direct Known Subclasses:
MinAreaRectTargetData, TargetListTargetData, UprightRectTargetData
public class TargetData extends Object
TargetData is a base class for target data sent by Deadeye camera pipelines.
